{"arkId":"cl010383090","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010383090","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Croix processionnelle","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Croix processionnelle"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : gothique (Occident-\u003Emoyen \u00e2ge)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1485 - 1500","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 505 - Corridor de Valence \/ Anne de Bretagne \/ Corridor de Faenza, Salle 505 - Anne de Bretagne, Vitrine 4","room":"Salle 505, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1485,"endYear":1500,"imprecision":"","text":"Fin du XVe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Anonyme","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q4233718"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 12870","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"croix processionnelle","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Cette grande croix aux extr\u00e9mit\u00e9s fleuronn\u00e9es porte un d\u00e9cor de feuilles d\u0027argent estamp\u00e9es dont les motifs sont identiques sur les deux faces. Les montants et traverses sont orn\u00e9s d\u0027un semis de fleurs de lys sur fond amati, qui laise place aux extr\u00e9mit\u00e9s \u00e0 des m\u00e9daillons quadrilob\u00e9s enfermant les symboles des \u00e9vang\u00e9listes tenant un phylact\u00e8re, pour s\u0027achever sur les extr\u00e9mit\u00e9s trilob\u00e9es par des rinceaux de roses largement \u00e9panouies. A la crois\u00e9e, la statuette du Christ est surmont\u00e9e d\u0027un soleil rayonnant. La crois\u00e9e est orn\u00e9e au revers d\u0027une statuette de la Vierge. Les statuettes du christ et de la Vierge sont partiellement dor\u00e9es, les quadrilobes et le soleil le sont enti\u00e8rement.","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; sur les phylact\u00e8res tenus par les symboles des \u00e9vang\u00e9listes : SANCTE MARCE ; SANCTE LUCA ; SANCTE IOHANNES ; SANCTE MATHIA\r ; Poin\u00e7on : \r ; sur la face lat\u00e9rale de la hampe : D minuscule gothique et un morif effac\u00e9 sous une couronne","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"50","displayDimension":"50 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"40","displayDimension":"40 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"1,8","displayDimension":"1,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nTechnique : estamp\u00e9 = estampage (techniques m\u00e9tal)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : bois (\u00e2me de bois)\r\nTechnique : dor\u00e9 = dorure (techniques m\u00e9tal) (partiellement)","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France) (?) ; Troyes (Champagne-Ardenne = Champagne Ardenne-\u003EAube) (?)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Kugel ; dation, 2016.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"dation","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date du conseil","value":"12\/11\/2015","startYear":2015,"endYear":2015},{"type":"date","value":"07\/12\/2015","startYear":2015,"endYear":2015},{"type":"date","value":"27\/01\/2016","startYear":2016,"endYear":2016},{"type":"date","value":"05\/04\/2016","startYear":2016,"endYear":2016},{"type":"date de l\u0027arr\u00eat\u00e9\/d\u00e9cision","value":"17\/06\/2016","startYear":2016,"endYear":2016},{"type":"date de l\u0027inscription sur l\u0027inventair